          <turn endTime="984.243" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="957.31"><s>&Icirc;n ceea ce- l prive&scedil;te ,<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fidel Castro</ENAMEX>este cel din_urm&abreve; supravie&tcedil;uitor politic .</s> <s>Oamenii i- au<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e1" eiid="ei415" eventID="e1" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">prezis</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e86" eiid="ei416" eventID="e86" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">demisia</EVENT>de at&acirc;tea ori , &scedil;i<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">SUA</ENAMEX>a<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e2" eiid="ei417" eventID="e2" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">&icirc;ncercat</EVENT>s- o<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e4" eiid="ei418" eventID="e4" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">gr&abreve;beasc&abreve;</EVENT>&icirc;n repetate r&acirc;nduri .</s> <s><ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Mereu</ENAMEX>el<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e87" eiid="ei419" eventID="e87" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">rezist&abreve;</EVENT>.</s> <s>A<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e7" eiid="ei420" eventID="e7" polarity="POS" pos="OTHER" tense="PRESENT">tr&abreve;it</EVENT>mai mult &scedil;i uneori a<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e8" eiid="ei421" eventID="e8" polarity="POS" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="PRESENT">fost</EVENT>mai inteligent dec&acirc;t<CARDINAL>opt</CARDINAL>pre&scedil;edin&tcedil;i americani .</s><s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fidel Castro</ENAMEX>l-a<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e9" eiid="ei422" eventID="e9" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PAST">invitat</EVENT>pe<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ioan Paul</ENAMEX>s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e11" eiid="ei423" eventID="e11" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">vin&abreve;</EVENT>cu un motiv .</s> <s>Aceasta este clar o oportunitate pentru<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Cuba</ENAMEX>s&abreve; arate bine pe plan interna&tcedil;ional .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="998.360" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="984.243"><s>&Icirc;ntreaga lume va<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="PERCEPTION" eid="e15" eiid="ei424" eventID="e15" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">vedea</EVENT>imagini de- ale<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Papei</ENAMEX>&icirc;n<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Cuba</ENAMEX>.</s> <s>Vor<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="PERCEPTION" eid="e16" eiid="ei425" eventID="e16" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">vedea</EVENT>imagini de- ale<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Papei</ENAMEX>cu<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fidel Castro</ENAMEX>.</s> <s>Va<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e18" eiid="ei426" eventID="e18" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">ar&abreve;ta</EVENT>restului lumii c&abreve;<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Cuba</ENAMEX>este<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e385" eiid="ei470" eventID="e385" polarity="POS" pos="OTHER" tense="PRESENT">ca</EVENT>oricare alt&abreve; na&tcedil;iune , ceva ce<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">SUA</ENAMEX>a<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e22" eiid="ei429" eventID="e22" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">&icirc;ncercat</EVENT>, desigur , s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e24" eiid="ei430" eventID="e24" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">demonstreze</EVENT>lumii c&abreve; nu e .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1010.902" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="998.360"><s><SIGNAL sid="s95">Pentru</SIGNAL><TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" mod="EQUAL_OR_LESS" temporalFunction="false" tid="t94" type="DURATION" value="P40Y">aproape<CARDINAL>patruzeci</CARDINAL>de ani</TIMEX3>,<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Statele_Unite</ENAMEX>au<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="REPORTING" eid="e26" eiid="ei431" eventID="e26" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spus</EVENT>categoric c&abreve; nu vor<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e99" eiid="ei432" eventID="e99" modality="would" polarity="NEG" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">tolera</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e97" eiid="ei433" eventID="e97" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">regimul</EVENT>totalitar &icirc;n propria -i curte .</s> <s><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e240" eiid="ei434" eventID="e240" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">Embargoul</EVENT>economic &scedil;i politic al<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">SUA</ENAMEX>a fost ceea_ce a<EVENT aspect="PERFECTIVE" class="ASPECTUAL" eid="e30" eiid="ei435" eventID="e30" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">&tcedil;inut</EVENT><ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Cuba</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e381" eiid="ei466" eventID="e381" polarity="POS" pos="PREPOSITION" tense="NONE">&icirc;ntr-</EVENT>o cutie .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1025.419" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1010.902">
            <s>Principalul motiv al lui<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Castro</ENAMEX>pentru a-l<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e32" eiid="ei437" eventID="e32" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">invita</EVENT>pe<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Pap&abreve;</ENAMEX>este , la nivel interna&tcedil;ional , s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e100" eiid="ei438" eventID="e100" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">poat&abreve;</EVENT><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e35" eiid="ei439" eventID="e35" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">spune</EVENT>restului lumii c&abreve; acest guvern nu e at&acirc;t de<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e382" eiid="ei467" eventID="e382" polarity="NEG" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">&icirc;nchis</EVENT>, de<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e383" eiid="ei468" eventID="e383" polarity="NEG" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="PRESENT">intolerant</EVENT>, sau de<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e384" eiid="ei469" eventID="e384" polarity="NEG" pos="NOUN" tense="PRESENT">totalitar</EVENT>pe_c&acirc;t &icirc;l<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e38" eiid="ei441" eventID="e38" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">fac</EVENT>unii s&abreve; par&abreve; .</s>
          </turn>
          <turn endTime="1038.683" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1025.419"><s>Unul dintre scenariile<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e103" eiid="ei442" eventID="e103" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PASTPART">avansate</EVENT>pe scar&abreve; larg&abreve;<SIGNAL sid="s43">&icirc;naintea</SIGNAL><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e42" eiid="ei443" eventID="e42" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">vizitei</EVENT>este c&abreve; prin<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Pap&abreve;</ENAMEX>,<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Cuba</ENAMEX>, &icirc;nc&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e44" eiid="ei444" eventID="e44" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PASTPART">condus&abreve;</EVENT>de<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Castro</ENAMEX>, poate<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="ASPECTUAL" eid="e45" eiid="ei445" eventID="e45" modality="can" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">&icirc;ncepe</EVENT>o<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e107" eiid="ei446" eventID="e107" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">rela&tcedil;ie</EVENT>mai productiv&abreve; cu lumea .</s> <s>Aceasta , &icirc;n_schimb , va<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e48" eiid="ei447" eventID="e48" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">aduce</EVENT>presiuni asupra<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Washingtonului</ENAMEX>s&abreve; se<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e50" eiid="ei448" eventID="e50" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">schimbe</EVENT>.</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1049.369" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1040.637">
            <s>Acei observatori care<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e51" eiid="ei449" eventID="e51" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESPART">caut&abreve;</EVENT>o<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e52" eiid="ei450" eventID="e52" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">lupt&abreve;</EVENT>&icirc;ntre reprezentan&tcedil;ii intransigen&tcedil;i &scedil;i ideologiile foarte diferite vor fi , cel mai probabil ,<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e53" eiid="ei451" eventID="e53" polarity="POS" pos="ADJECTIVE" tense="FUTURE">dezam&abreve;gi&tcedil;i</EVENT>.</s>
          </turn>
          <turn endTime="1064.200" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1051.155"><s><ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Castro</ENAMEX>a spus c&abreve; po&tcedil;i fi comunist &scedil;i_totu&scedil;i s&abreve; fii cre&scedil;tin .</s> <s>El<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="REPORTING" eid="e56" eiid="ei452" eventID="e56" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">spune</EVENT>c&abreve; el &scedil;i<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Papa</ENAMEX><EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e57" eiid="ei453" eventID="e57" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="PRESENT">vor</EVENT>am&acirc;ndoi s&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="ASPECTUAL" eid="e59" eiid="ei454" eventID="e59" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="INFINITIVE">pun&abreve;</EVENT>cap&abreve;t<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e60" eiid="ei455" eventID="e60" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">exploat&abreve;rii</EVENT>omului de_c&abreve;tre om .</s> <s>&Icirc;ntrebarea este pe cine vor<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="STATE" eid="e378" eiid="ei456" eventID="e378" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">crede</EVENT>cubanezii ?</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1082.531" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1064.200"><s>Principalul fapt negativ este<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_STATE" eid="e109" eiid="ei457" eventID="e109" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="PRESENT">riscul</EVENT>c&abreve;<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e63" eiid="ei458" eventID="e63" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">vizita</EVENT><ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Papei</ENAMEX>va<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="I_ACTION" eid="e64" eiid="ei459" eventID="e64" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="FUTURE">convinge</EVENT>mult mai mul&tcedil;i cubanezi s&abreve; se<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e66" eiid="ei460" eventID="e66" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="INFINITIVE">elibereze</EVENT>de guvernul cubanez .</s> <s><SIGNAL sid="s110">Dac&abreve;</SIGNAL>e a&scedil;a , atunci<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e67" eiid="ei461" eventID="e67" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">vizita</EVENT><ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Papei</ENAMEX>ar<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="ASPECTUAL" eid="e112" eiid="ei462" eventID="e112" modality="would" polarity="POS" pos="VERB" tense="NONE">deschide</EVENT>realmente un nou capitol &icirc;n<EVENT aspect="NONE" class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e69" eiid="ei463" eventID="e69" polarity="POS" pos="NOUN" tense="NONE">rela&tcedil;iile</EVENT>guvernului cu propria -i societate .</s> <s>Pentru guvernul cubanez , acesta este riscul .</s></turn>
          <turn endTime="1094.00" speaker="unknown" spkrType="unknown" startTime="1085.323"><s>La sf&acirc;r&scedil;itul transmisiunii din aceast&abreve; sear&abreve; , &icirc;nc&abreve; o excursie &icirc;n_jurul<ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Havanei</ENAMEX>pentru a vedea cum arat&abreve; fa&tcedil;&abreve;_de data trecut&abreve; .</s> <s>&Scedil;i &icirc;ntr- un scurt<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">moment Diane Sawyer</ENAMEX>va avea alte &scedil;tiri .</s></turn>
